         <div>
            <head>"YOUTH"</head>
            
            <lg>
               <l>We have to-morrow</l>
               <l>Bright before us</l>
               <l>Like a flame</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l>Yesterday, a night-gone thing</l>
               <l>A sun-down name</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l>And dawn to-day</l>
               <l>Broad arch above the road we came,</l>
               <l>We march!</l>
            </lg>

            <byline>-Langston Hughes</byline>
         </div>
      </body>
